OL,3,CManchester United to make 'up to 250
OL,4,Cstaff redundant' in bid to cut costs
OL,6,FManchester United have told staff that
OL,7,Fup to 250 people are set to be made
OL,8,Fredundant as part of sweeping cuts, it
OL,9,Fis understood.
OL,11,FBritish billionaire Sir Jim Ratcliffe
OL,12,Fcompleted his purchase of a 27.7%
OL,13,Fstake in the Premier League club for
OL,14,F#1.25billion in February.
OL,16,FIneos took charge of football
OL,17,Foperations as part of the agreement
OL,18,Fand commissioned a cost review as they
OL,19,Fmoved to change things behind the
OL,20,Fscenes as well as on the field.
