OL,3,CManchester United to make 'up to 250
OL,4,Cstaff redundant' in bid to cut costs
OL,6,FIt is understood staff were told at a
OL,7,Fmeeting on Wednesday that around 250
OL,8,Fof the circa 1,100-strong workforce
OL,9,Fwill be part of the club-wide
OL,10,Fredundancy programme.
OL,12,FThe club believe a restructuring is
OL,13,Fneeded, especially in an era of new
OL,14,Ffinancial regulations, and feel the
OL,15,Fstaffing level does not reflect their
OL,16,Fcurrent performance level on the field.
OL,18,FAll departments and levels are
OL,19,Faffected apart from the Manchester
OL,20,FUnited Foundation.
