OL,3,CManchester United to make 'up to 250
OL,4,Cstaff redundant' in bid to cut costs
OL,6,FThe move to cut nearly a quarter of
OL,7,Fstaff has been met by understandable
OL,8,Fanger and anxiety by United employees.
OL,10,FThis is the biggest among a number of
OL,11,Fchanges since Ratcliffe's arrival at
OL,12,FOld Trafford.
OL,14,FUnited employees were informed towards
OL,15,Fthe end of last season that hybrid
OL,16,Fworking would stop from 1 June, while
OL,17,Fsome customary benefits were stripped
OL,18,Fin relation to the FA Cup final.
