OL,3,CManchester United to make 'up to 250
OL,4,Cstaff redundant' in bid to cut costs
OL,6,FNon-football staff were then offered
OL,7,Fthe chance to leave in a proposal that
OL,8,Fwould see them receive a fast-tracked
OL,9,Fpayment of a bonus due in September.
OL,11,FThis latest move leaves staff worrying
OL,12,Fabout their future just six weeks out
OL,13,Ffrom United's Premier League opener
OL,14,Fagainst Fulham.
